    "comments": [
      "Information of tracklisting from Hal C F Astell's website.",
      "Hal: \"Show listing is almost complete but my recording cuts out before the end of the Rush track. Necrophagia are also mentioned so may be the closeout track. Date very likely. Comments identify this as certainly being before 15 Feb 1987 because of an upcoming gig and all other dates in range are confirmed for other shows. Stereo Sequence trailers for the first part of the Richard Branson/Virgin story suggest that this is a week before the 23 Jan 1987 show.\""
    ]
